The paper deals with complexity classes and their properties, which suggests that it belongs to cs.CC (Computational Complexity). The use of Banach-Mazur games and probabilistic classes such as BPP suggests a connection to information theory (cs.IT) and probability theory (cs.DS). The mention of meager comeager laws and Baire categories suggests a connection to mathematical logic (cs.LO) and set theory (cs.CE).
